resolution: Shipped lintExtensionBlueprint + assertExtensionBlueprint for author-time blueprint preflight.
expected_result: "Capability drift / duplicate / empty-surface footguns are caught at edit/test time, not at activation."
actual_result: "Both helpers added with structured findings, legacy-alias resolution, barrel + /sdk/testing exports, docs, 100% coverage."
